{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/the-watcher-novel-sieg-aegis-synchrona/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"The Watcher: Novel Epik Dari Author Komik Synchrona","content":"\n<p>Kamu sudah baca komik <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Synchrona (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/synchrona\" target=\"_blank\">Synchrona</a> di CIAYO Comics? Komik action-mystery ini menampilkan petualangan menegangkan dari Saga Delphi dan kawan-kawannya melawan monster Desire serta memecahkan kasus pembunuhan yang berhubungan dengan media sosial Facetruth. Per bulan maret ini, komik CIAYO Class karangan Sieg Aegis dan RIzukiaeru ini telah disubscribe lebih dari 3 ribu orang loh!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53412\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/the-watcher-novel-sieg-aegis-synchrona/attachment/01-the-watcher/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-the-watcher.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-the-watcher\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-the-watcher-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-the-watcher.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-the-watcher.jpg\" alt=\"Synchrona. Sumber: Sieg Aegis / CIAYO Comics\" class=\"wp-image-53412\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-the-watcher.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/01-the-watcher-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Synchrona. Sumber: Sieg Aegis / CIAYO Comics</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Tapi tahu nggak, author Sieg Aegis nggak cuma dikenal lewat\nSynchrona saja loh. Sebelumnya, dia sudah aktif berkarya dengan menciptakan\nnovel berjudul The Watcher. The Watcher merupakan novel karangan Sieg Aegis\nyang dalam karya ini menggunakan nama Gisantya Nuansa Dwi Pratama. Novel ini\nbercerita tentang kelompok misterius yang membimbing takdir manusia melalui\nberbagai petunjuk hidup yang dikehendaki atau telah digariskan. </p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53413\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/the-watcher-novel-sieg-aegis-synchrona/attachment/02-the-watcher/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-the-watcher.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-the-watcher\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-the-watcher-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-the-watcher.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-the-watcher.jpg\" alt=\"The Watcher. Sumber: Sieg Aegis\" class=\"wp-image-53413\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-the-watcher.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02-the-watcher-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>The Watcher. Sumber: Sieg Aegis</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Dalam cerita The Watcher, manusia digambarkan sulit menyelesaikan masalah yang sedang dihadapi akibat dikuasai ego sehingga tidak mendapatkan petunjuk hidup dan terjebak dalam kesesatan abadi. Manusia membutuhkan pihak lain untuk menyelesaikan masalahnya. Cerita novel ini mengambil latar waktu tahun 1900 di mana masih berhubungan dengan sejarah di masa lalu maupun kejadian penting di masa sekarang. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Novel ini banyak mengambil referensi mitologi, okultisme, serta spiritual sebagai unsur intrinsik cerita yang dikemas ringan. Keunikan dari cerita The Watcher adalah pihak protagonis yang merepresentasikan pembaca sementara tokoh asli cerita sebagai pihak ketiga. Pihak antagonis dalam cerita ini merupakan takdir atau permasalahan yang dihadapi pembaca. Sehingga gagasan utama cerita ini adalah untuk membantu permasalahan yang dihadapi pembaca.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53414\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/the-watcher-novel-sieg-aegis-synchrona/attachment/03-the-watcher/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-the-watcher.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-the-watcher\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-the-watcher-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-the-watcher.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-the-watcher.jpg\" alt=\"Karyamesta. Sumber: Sieg Aegis\" class=\"wp-image-53414\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-the-watcher.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03-the-watcher-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Karyamesta. Sumber: Sieg Aegis</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Selain cerita utama, The Watcher juga memiliki beberapa cerita\nsampingan seperti Karyamesta yang bergenre slice of life, The Phantom Pedal\nyang bergenre dewasa, hingga The Fear Frame yang bergenre horror. Dan yang\nlebih menarik lagi, komik Synchrona di CIAYO Comics juga merupakan bagian dari\ndunia The Watcher itu sendiri!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Masih belum penasaran dengan kisah The Watcher? Mungkin rekomendasi dari komikus Sweta Kartika bisa membantu kamu membuat keputusan. “The Watcher adalah sebuah kitab suci yang hidup,” ungkap author <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Lovebirds Diary (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic/lovebirds-diary\" target=\"_blank\">Lovebirds Diary</a> dan <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Journal of Terror (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/journal-of-terror-komik-horror-mencekam/\" target=\"_blank\">Journal of Terror</a> ini. Kalau kamu suka Synchrona, pokoknya harus baca novel ini deh, biar makin paham dengan dunianya!</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img data-attachment-id=\"53415\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/the-watcher-novel-sieg-aegis-synchrona/attachment/04-the-watcher/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-the-watcher.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-the-watcher\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-the-watcher-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-the-watcher.jpg\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-the-watcher.jpg\" alt=\"Beberapa buku dari dunia The Watcher. Sumber: Sieg Aegis\" class=\"wp-image-53415\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-the-watcher.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/04-the-watcher-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><figcaption>Beberapa buku dari dunia The Watcher. Sumber: Sieg Aegis</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Kamu bisa membaca kisah The Watcher melalui buku fisik maupun melalui website. Untuk membaca via web, kamu bisa mengunjungi <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"http://www.thewatcherpro.com/\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.thewatcherpro.com/</a>. Jika kamu tertarik membaca novel fisiknya, kamu bisa memesannya langsung ke Sieg Aegis melalui Facebook (baik via <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/thewatcherpro/\" target=\"_blank\">fanpage</a> atau <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/gisantya\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">akun pribadi</a>), atau Whatsapp di 085640540570</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"09790461-3be5-5375-951d-3590cf360690"}}}